1. Execute benchmark_sim.sh and look for the elapsed time for different 
   backends, and compute the time per step, and make sure the problem
   sizes are appropriate.

2. Execute run_sim.sh to kick off a long running job that dumps
   out the post-processing quantities

3. Executre make_plots.sh to create png

4. Execute make_gifs.py to create the stacked gif in the images_stacked
   directory 
